Package: mutt
Title: A Microbial Scale Repository for Paired Microbiome Sequence Count Data with Total Abundance Measurements
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R:
    c(
      person("Maxwell", "Konnaris",
             email = "mak6930@psu.edu",
             role = c("aut", "cre")),
      person("Justin", "Silverman",
             email = "JustinSilverman@psu.edu",
             role = c("aut", "ctb"))
    )
Description: Parses and formats individual studies containing microbiome sequence count data
    paired with total abundance measurements (flow cytometry, ddPCR, qPCR, etc.), and returns
    a single data object containing selected studies.
